title: seg fault on import caffe2.python.onnx.backend
body_html:
I am seeing a seg fault for the following snippet:

>>> import caffe2.python.onnx.backend as backend
Segmentation fault (core dumped)

The versions of caffe2, pytorch and protobuf are:

# packages in environment at /root/anaconda3:
#
# Name                    Version                   Build  Channel
pytorch                   0.4.1           py36_py35_py27__9.0.176_7.1.2_2    pytorch
# packages in environment at /root/anaconda3:
#
# Name                    Version                   Build  Channel
caffe2-cuda9.0-cudnn7     0.8.dev         py36_2018.08.26    caffe2
# packages in environment at /root/anaconda3:
#
# Name                    Version                   Build  Channel
libprotobuf               3.6.0                hdbcaa40_0
protobuf                  3.5.1                    py36_3    conda-forge
